<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Doktor Yorumları</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.15.4/css/all.min.css"
    integrity="sha512-**********" crossorigin="anonymous" />
  </script>
  <script defer src="/js/getComments.js"></script>
</head>

<body>

  <%- include("partials/_header.ejs") %>

    <div class="container mt-5">
      <h1 class="mb-4">Doktor Yorumları</h1>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-12 mb-4">
          <div class="card">
            <div class="card-body">
              <img src="Alperen.jpg" alt="" style="width: 100px; border-radius: 15px;">
              <h5 class="card-title">Ord.Prof.Uzm.Dr. Alperen Erdoğan</h5>
              <p class="card-text">Grip, mevsimsel olarak yaygın bir hastalıktır. Özellikle kış aylarında, hijyen
                kurallarına dikkat ederek ve grip aşısı yaptırarak hastalıktan korunabilirsiniz.</p>
              <hr>
              <div class="container">
                <div class="bg-dark text-white text-center py-2 mt-5">
                  <h2>Yorumlar</h2>

                </div>
                <div id="doctor-1"></div>
                <div class="row">
                  <div class="col-md-6 col-sm-12">
                    <div>
                      <iframe
                        src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d391768.355431781!2d32.48257158608294!3d39.90356622124967!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x14d347d520732db1%3A0xbdc57b0c0842b8d!2sAnkara%2C+T%C3%BCrkiye!5e0!3m2!1str!2sus!4v1556530231994!5m2!1str!2sus"
                        width="100%" height="435" frameborder="0" style="border:0" allowfullscreen></iframe>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="col-md-6 col-sm-12">
                    <form action="/comments/create/doctor-1" method="post">
                      <div class="card mt-4">
                        <div class="card-body p-3">
                          <div class="form-group">
                            <div class="input-group mb-2">
                              <div class="input-group-prepend">
                                <div class="input-group-text">
                                  <i class="fa fa-user text-info"></i>
                                </div>
                              </div>
                              <input type="text" class="form-control" name="username" placeholder="Ad Soyad" required
                                id="AlpYorumAdSoyad">
                            </div>
                          </div>
                          <div class="form-group">
                            <div class="input-group mb-2">
                              <div class="input-group-prepend">
                                <div class="input-group-text">
                                  <i class="fa fa-envelope text-info"></i>
                                </div>
                              </div>
                              <input type="email" class="form-control" name="email" placeholder="E-Posta" required
                                id="AlpYorumEposta">
                            </div>
                          </div>
                          <div class="form-group">
                            <div class="input-group mb-2">
                              <div class="input-group-prepend">
                                <div class="input-group-text">
                                  <i class="fa fa-tag text-info"></i>
                                </div>
                              </div>
                              <input type="text" class="form-control" name="title" placeholder="Başlık" required
                                id="AlpYorumBaslik">
                            </div>
                          </div>
                          <div class="form-group">
                            <div class="input-group mb-2">
                              <div class="input-group-prepend">
                                <div class="input-group-text">
                                  <i class="fa fa-comment text-info"></i>
                                </div>
                              </div>
                              <textarea class="form-control" placeholder="Yorum..." rows="6" required name="text"
                                id="AlpYorumIcerik"></textarea>
                            </div>
                          </div>
                          <div class="text-center">
                            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-dark btn-block">gönder</button>
                          </div>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                    </form>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>

            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-12">
          <div class="card">
            <div class="card-body">
              <img src="furkan.jpg" alt="" style="width: 100px; height: 160px; border-radius: 15px;">
              <h5 class="card-title">Dr. Furkan Yılmaz</h5>
              <p class="card-text">Migren atakları genellikle belirli tetikleyici faktörlerle ilişkilidir. Bu faktörler
                genellikle başın ön kısmında görülmektedir.
              </p>

              <hr>

              <div class="container">
                <div class="bg-dark text-white text-center py-2 mt-5">
                  <h2>Yorumlar</h2>
                </div>
                <div id="doctor-2"></div>
                <div class="row">
                  <div class="col-md-6 col-sm-12">
                    <div>
                      <iframe
                        src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d391768.355431781!2d32.48257158608294!3d39.90356622124967!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x14d347d520732db1%3A0xbdc57b0c0842b8d!2sAnkara%2C+T%C3%BCrkiye!5e0!3m2!1str!2sus!4v1556530231994!5m2!1str!2sus"
                        width="100%" height="435" frameborder="0" style="border:0" allowfullscreen></iframe>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="col-md-6 col-sm-12">
                    <form action="/comments/create/doctor-2" method="post">
                      <div class="card mt-4">
                        <div class="card-body p-3">
                          <div class="form-group">
                            <div class="input-group mb-2">
                              <div class="input-group-prepend">
                                <div class="input-group-text">
                                  <i class="fa fa-user text-info"></i>
                                </div>
                              </div>
                              <input type="text" class="form-control" name="username" placeholder="Ad Soyad" required
                                id="SirazYorumAdSoyad">
                            </div>
                          </div>
                          <div class="form-group">
                            <div class="input-group mb-2">
                              <div class="input-group-prepend">
                                <div class="input-group-text">
                                  <i class="fa fa-envelope text-info"></i>
                                </div>
                              </div>
                              <input type="email" class="form-control" name="email" placeholder="E-Posta" required
                                id="SirazYorumEposta">
                            </div>
                          </div>
                          <div class="form-group">
                            <div class="input-group mb-2">
                              <div class="input-group-prepend">
                                <div class="input-group-text">
                                  <i class="fa fa-tag text-info"></i>
                                </div>
                              </div>
                              <input type="text" class="form-control" name="title" placeholder="Başlık" required
                                id="SirazYorumBaslik">
                            </div>
                          </div>
                          <div class="form-group">
                            <div class="input-group mb-2">
                              <div class="input-group-prepend">
                                <div class="input-group-text">
                                  <i class="fa fa-comment text-info"></i>
                                </div>
                              </div>
                              <textarea class="form-control" placeholder="Yorum..." rows="6" required name="text"
                                id="SirazYorumIcerik"></textarea>
                            </div>
                          </div>
                          <div class="text-center">
                            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-dark btn-block">gönder</button>

                          </div>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                    </form>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>

            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <footer>
      <%- include("partials/_footer.ejs") %>
    </footer>
    <style>
      /* Footer Style */
      footer {
        color: #ffffff;
      }

      ul {
        padding: 0px;
      }

      ol,
      ul {
        margin-bottom: 0px;
      }

      .social-icon {
        padding: 0;
        margin-bottom: 0px;
        float: right;
      }

      .social-icon li {
        list-style: none;
        display: inline-block;
      }

      .social-icon li i {
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #262725;
        border: solid 2px #ffffff;
        height: 31px;
        width: 31px;
        text-align: center;
        vertical-align: middle;
        border-radius: 100px;
        line-height: 27px;
        margin-right: 15px;
        transition: 1s;
        background: #fff;
      }

      .social-icon li i:hover {
        border: solid 2px #272525;
        color: #ffffff;
        background: #262725;
      }

      .phone-no i {
        position: relative;
        margin-right: 14px;
        font-size: 43px;
        top: 5px;
      }

      .phone-no {
        margin-top: -22px;
        text-align: right;
      }

      .footer-day-time {
        padding-bottom: 30px;
        border-bottom: 2px solid #7a6f6f;
        padding-top: 14px;
        margin-bottom: 55px;
      }

      .footer-day-time ul li {
        display: inline;
        margin-right: 20px;
      }

      .footer-day-time ul li:last-child {
        margin-right: 0px;
      }

      .phone-no a {
        color: #fff;
        font-family: PlayfairDisplay-Black;
        font-size: 34px;
        font-weight: bold;
      }

      .footer-top {
        background: #292828;

        padding: 30px 0;
        /* Örneğin, yukarıdaki 50px 0 50px olan padding değerlerini 30px 0 olarak azaltabilirsiniz */

      }

      .footer-top h4 {
        font-size: 19px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        margin-bottom: 30px;
      }

      .footer-top p {
        font-size: 13px;
        line-height: 2;
      }

      footer p {
        margin-bottom: 0;
      }

      .footer-logo {
        display: block;
        margin-bottom: 32px;
      }

      .address1 li {
        list-style: none;
        position: relative;
        padding: 0px 0 14px 34px;
        line-height: 26px;
      }

      ul.address1 span {
        position: absolute;
        width: 40px;
        max-width: 40px;
        left: 0;
      }

      .address1 li a {
        color: #fff;
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      ul.address1 i {
        width: 20px;
        position: absolute;
        left: 0px;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 28px;
        top: 0;
      }

      ul.address1 i.fa-envelope {
        font-size: 18px;
        top: 4px;
      }

      footer ul.social-icon {
        float: left;
      }

      footer .social-icon li i:hover {
        background: #000000;
        border-color: #000000;
      }

      .footer-bottom {
        background: #000000;
        padding: 5px 0;
      }

      .footer-bottom ul li {
        display: inline;
        margin-right: 20px;
        font-size: 18px;
      }

      .footer-bottom ul li a {
        color: #fff;
      }

      .footer-bottom ul {
        float: right;
      }

      .footer-bottom ul li:last-child {
        margin-right: 0;
      }

      .copyright {
        font-size: 18px;
      }

      .footer-day-time ul li,
      .address1 li {
        margin-right: 10px;
        /* İçerik öğeleri arasındaki margin değerlerini azaltabilirsiniz */
      }
    </style>

</body>

</html>